<h3>Your payment has expired</h3>
<p>Your pending payment for <%= Pay.application_name %> has expired. This usually happens when the payment was not completed within the allotted time window.</p>
<p>Please initiate a new payment or update your billing information to continue.</p>
<p><%= link_to "Update billing information", root_url %></p>
<p>Let us know if you have any questions.</p>
<p>— The <%= Pay.application_name %> Team</p>
